   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Abir&apos;s Garden Playgrounds for a Safe Place to Grow</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Combatants for Peace (C4P) are building playgrounds and organizing children&apos;s theater programs in memory of a child, Abir, who touched so many hearts. The playgrounds, all connected with a Palestinian kindergarten or elementary school in the West Bank, are constructed by professionals with Israeli and Palestinian former combatants working together to help.  New, the C4P teams are coaching children&apos;s theater programs at each school to help youth raise awareness of their village&apos;s story.</narrative>
  </description>
